 \sum\limits_{n=0}^\infty \frac{n}{3^n}=\frac{3}{4}
L
L=\sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{n}{3^n}=\sum_{n=1}^\infty  \frac{n}{3^n}= \frac{1}{3}\sum_{n=1}^\infty  \frac{n}{3^{n-1}}=  \frac{1}{3}\sum_{n=0}^\infty  \frac{n+1}{3^{n}}= \frac{1}{3}\left[\sum_{n=0}^\infty  \frac{n}{3^{n}}+\sum_{n=0}^\infty  \frac{1}{3^{n}}\right] =\frac{1}{3}\left[L+ \sum_{n=0}^\infty  \frac{1}{3^{n}}\right].
